replies.msg:
Klopp on VAR: &quot;I don't think there has been any games without any issues. In Germany, in first part of this season there was a lot of irritation with it too. But now it's much more settled. It will take time.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp on VAR: &quot;In our game against West Brom it took too long to make decisions.&quot;

Klopp: &ldquo;I think Liverpool is a really interesting project at the moment.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &ldquo;There are a lot of good football clubs around. We cannot convince them [signings] with money, we do it with the football we play, the way we treat them. I think it's a really interesting project in this moment here.&rdquo;

Benitez: &ldquo;I have a lot of friends here, fans, people around the city, it makes it a little bit special.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Benitez: &ldquo;You play against Liverpool, they have a lot of possession, you have to play counter-attack, how many is the key.&rdquo;

